<br>
I strongly suggest not putting more than 10 points into any stat, its poor point utilization.  Then again, so is 50 weapon spec, but that's a different discussion.<br>
<br>
Your stat spec is fine, but you may just want to go str/con/cha - they are your class stats for a reason.  Some that go troll might pump up dex/qui to offset...each to his own.<br>
<br>
with 39/46/26 spec, with items, ranks, and mastery of parry, you can get over 50 spec in parry, in case you're going kobold with high parry/dex.<br>
<br>
